data.description: Step into your dream home in the beautiful Copper Creek community in Fort Worth! Entertaining is a breeze in this open-concept home, where the spacious kitchen boasts modern appliances and quartz countertops. The master bedroom is a true retreat, featuring an en-suite bathroom with double vanities, a soaking tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. The separate office space offers a quiet sanctuary that can easily double as an extra bedroom for guests or a growing family. Step outside to the covered patio and spacious backyard! This home has been impeccably maintained, ensuring that all you need to do is move in and start making memories! Living in Copper Creek means enjoying a resort-style lifestyle every day. Take a dip in the pool, relax at the clubhouse, or enjoy a leisurely stroll along the walking trails. With a splash pad and basketball courts, there's never a dull moment in this vibrant community!
